                  <handDesc>
                     
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Fine, regular.</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red (luminous vivid red; name of the owner in light
                           brilliant vermillion).</seg>
                        <date>Mid-18th – mid-19th century.</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ብ</abbr> for <expan>ብሂል </expan> (<locus target="#6v">6v</locus>, 7r).</item>
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ሀ፡/ኀ፡ እግ፡ በኃ፡ ዝን፡ አስ</abbr> for <expan>ሀበነ፡/ኀበነ እግዚአብሔር፡ በኃይለ፡
                                 ዝንቱ፡ አስማቲከ </expan> (e.g., <locus target="#13r">13r</locus>, 13v,
                              14r, 14v).</item>
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ኢየ፡ ክር፡</abbr> for <expan>ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ </expan> (e.g., <locus target="#46r">46r</locus>, 47r).</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; the name of the owner; two groups of
                           lines alternating with black lines on the incipit page of Texts I and II;
                           the incipit of the subsections in Text I; elements of the punctuation
                           signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <desc type="findingAid">Weekly readings are indicated by the name of the
                              weekday in the upper margin: ዘሠሉስ: <locus target="#7r">fol. 7r</locus>
                              ሠረቀ፡ ረቡዕ: <locus target="#17v">fol. 17v</locus>. ሠረቀ፡ ሐሙስ: <locus target="#28r">fol. 28r</locus> ሠረቀ፡ ዓርብ፡ : <locus target="#32r">fol. 32r</locus> (and interlineally) ሠረቀ፡ ቀዳም: <locus target="#35v">fol. 35v</locus>
                           </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3">
                           <desc>- The word sämay is decorated with red and black dots, above and below: <locus target="#15v">fol.  15v</locus>. - Erasures marked with thin lines above and below a word: <locus target="#36r">fol.  36r</locus>. - Immediate correction marked with thin lines above and below a word: <locus target="#15v">fol.  15v</locus>. - A crude, recent drawing on the inner side of the front board. - A crude, recent coloured (red, blue) drawing of a human figure: <locus target="#49v">fol.  49v</locus>. - Spaces for rubricated names left unfilled: fols. 18v, 19r, 19v, 20r, 20v, 21v, 42r. - Crude notes and scribbles: fols. 1v, 2r, 2v, 3r, 48v, 49r, 49v, 52r, 58v, 59r, 59v.</desc>
                        </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
